plot: Join Dora and Boots as they face knights, dragons, magicians, and more on a double-length epic adventure to save the Crystal Kingdom from a greedy king! Then help Dora on a school day adventure AND fix Boots' out-of-control banana wish!
title: Dora Saves the Crystal Kingdom
